headline: Elevance Steps In As UnitedHealth Delays — Will It Set The Tone For Insurers?
summary: Health insurer Elevance Health Inc. (NYSE:ELV) is scheduled to release its second quarter 2025 financial results on July 17. Analysts estimate adjusted earnings of $9.197 per share on sales of $48.24 billion, as per data from Benzinga Pro. UnitedHealth Group Inc. (NYSE:UNH) has been the first major health insurer to report quarterly earnings for several quarters.
